						<summary>

						<p>The inscription is badly mutilated and damaged. It seems to record some provision made by the <hi rend="italic">Sabhā</hi> of the place for (special) offerings and worship to god Tirumāliruñjōlai-Dēvar on the day of Uttirāḍam in the Āḍi month.</p>						

